  <!-- EN: vulture flock -->
  <RM_VultureFlock.label>秃鹫群</RM_VultureFlock.label>
  <RM_VultureFlock.letterLabel>秃鹫群</RM_VultureFlock.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Drawn by multiple broken mechanoids in the area, a squad of vultures are approaching to salvage their machinery. They aren’t intent on fighting and will leave once the resources are retrieved or if they can’t retrieve their objective peacefully within a day. -->
  <RM_VultureFlock.letterText>被该区域多个破碎的机械人吸引，一队秃鹫正在靠近打捞它们的机械。它们并不打算战斗，一旦资源回收完毕或一天内无法和平回收目标，它们就会离开。</RM_VultureFlock.letterText>
  <!-- EN: wandering mechanoids -->
  <RM_WanderingMechanoids.label>流浪机械人</RM_WanderingMechanoids.label>
  <RM_WanderingMechanoids.letterLabel>游荡的机械人</RM_WanderingMechanoids.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Fleeing from a conflict, a group of mechanoids are passing through the area in search of repairs. They will try to avoid further endangering themselves and will only attack in self defence. -->
  <RM_WanderingMechanoids.letterText>一群机械人从冲突中逃离，途经该地区寻找修理。它们会尽量避免进一步危及自己，只会在自卫时发动攻击。</RM_WanderingMechanoids.letterText>
